    Friends / Group places in & outside India
    </h1>
    <p>
      There is something surreal about covering milestones with people who love the journey as much as you do. Whether the journey is as swift as the wind or as bumpy as a camel ride, traveling has not only led to many friendships but also has strengthened the existing ones. Moreover, there are some destinations that clearly live up to the statement of the more the merrier. Hence, they are best visited with friends or in groups. There are many places to visit with friends in and outside India that are often in the bucket list of many travelers and are a prompt mention in every friend circle. Mentioned below is a list of many such places that you can book a tour.
    </p>
    <h2>Best Places To Travel With Friends Around The World</h2>

    <h3>Thailand</h3>

    <div class="kerala">
      <img src="kerala1.jpg" alt="img" height="150px" width="270px" />
