    <p>
      The best of cityscape paired with lip-smacking cuisine and a tropical background is just the kind of ambience this country beholds. There is no magical place than Singapore to treat yourself with a fun-filled package of lavish and eccentric. From tropical themed garden and idyllic islands to bewildering skyscrapers and market places, Singapore has a lot that is just perfect for a getaway with friends. The area of this place offers such vibrant contrast between temples and skyscrapers and concrete marvels to breathtaking islands that no matter how diversified your group may be it will always be a good choice. Moreover, you will find some of the best places to visit with friends around the world all in Singapore such as Sentosa Island, Singapore Botanic Garden, Universal Studios, Buddha Tooth Relic Temple, Madame Tussauds Museum, Helix Bridge, etc.
    </p>

    <h3>Hong Kong</h3>

